                    <span>In the not too distant future, this book will eclipse Clausewitz's On War. Van Creveld's work truly explains a major on-going transformation of warfare--a transformation we are having a hard time dealing with.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Start with the ending</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>3</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
